original_title: Striped Bass Super Highway: Cape Cod Canal
overview: Heading up the east coast to fish the top-water baits along the Cape Cod Canal in Cape Cod, Massachusetts for some of the most incredible striped bass fishing in the world.  We’re joined by “The Fish Whisperer” himself Roy Leyva. The canal opened in 1914 and has been producing some of the best stripe bass fishing to be found anywhere in the world since then. Non-stop action.
title: Striped Bass Super Highway: Cape Cod Canal
